Established relationships between dimension and fact tables.

4. DAX Measures Created

Total Revenue = SUM(Fact_Sales[Revenue])

Total Orders = DISTINCTCOUNT(Fact_Sales[Order ID])

Total Discount = SUM(Fact_Sales[Discount Amount])

Total Quantity = SUM(Fact_Sales[Quantity])

Total GMV = SUM(Fact_Sales[GMV])

Average Order Value =
DIVIDE([Total Revenue],[Total Orders],0)

